&kp C_MUTE     &kp LCTRL  &none   &lt 1 ESC  &mt LEFT_SHIFT TAB  &lt 3 SPACE    &none            &lt 3 SPACE  &lt 3 SPACE  &lt 4 BACKSPACE  &kp RIGHT_GUI  &none
            >;

