            bindings = <
&trans       &trans   &trans  &trans  &trans  &soft_off            &trans  &soft_off          &rgb_ug RGB_SPI   &rgb_ug RGB_SAI    &rgb_ug RGB_COLOR_HSB(114,100,50)  &bt BT_CLR                      &bt BT_CLR_ALL
