&trans  &kp TILDE              &kp AMPERSAND    &kp ASTERISK  &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp DOUBLE_QUOTES    &trans  &kp GRAVE  &kp N7  &kp N8  &kp N9  &kp APOS   &trans
